welcome.aboutText:
Project Management App is your powerful tool to maximize project's efficiency with Kanban boards. 

 Kanban-board - is a visual tool, that helps in monitoring current organisation's state and simplifies team communication. 

 Benefits: 
 - Gives a clear picture of what needs to be accomplished and when; 
 - Visual - everyone on the same page; 
 - Reduces the risk of errors and duplication of effort; 
 - Helps teams to identify and reduce bottlenecks in their workflows; 
 - Brings improved delivery speed, predictability and increased customer satisfaction as a result.
